🦌🛷🎅🏼Sleigh All Day … It’s Almost Christmas!!

Tips On How Can You Reduce Holiday Stress To Better Enjoy The Magical Season:
👉🏽Be picky over parties - only go to the ones you can & want to attend. 
👉🏽Treat Yourself but prioritize healthy eating. 
👉🏽Cut out clutter before you decorate. 
👉🏽Rest up to reap the benefits of stage 4 sleep. 
👉🏽Do something physical every day. 
👉🏽If travelling pack in advance. 
👉🏽Shop for deals & don’t put too much pressure on yourself with gifts - not what it’s really about
👉🏽It’s cuddle season, get intimate! It boosts your immune system, alleviates pain and makes you feel happier - all the things you need to get through the busy season!
👉🏽Ask for help when you need it. 

AND MOST IMPORTANTLY DONT SWEAT THE SMALL SHIT!!!!

💥Here We Go Again💥

👊🏽👙10 Week Summer Shred!!!

⬅️Beginning of my first serious summer shred in March 2018 (5 Years Ago) at an average weight of 135lbs 
➡️Beginning of my current summer shred March 20 2023 at an average weight of 145lbs

You’re Always Doing Better Than You Think You Are…

But hey, It’s hard when you pull out your summer bikinis and they don’t fit like they did last summer 😅 so… look back further, look back to where it started, at how far you’ve come and allow yourself to be proud of that process. 

Do you remember all the obstacles you faced to get you to where you are now, all the physical and mental battles you’ve won and all the fears you’ve overcome?

When You Think About How Far You’ve Come Today You Can Have Faith In How Much Further Youll Go Tomorrow 🫶🏽

🧠☂️Your mental health is the umbrella that shelters you in every aspect of your life. Your success in anything starts in your brain... Period. 

➖So, what have you done for your Mental Health lately?➖

🏋🏼‍♀️Exercise not only changes your body, is changes your mind, attitude and mood. 

🌊Being near water creates relaxation, improves brain health and relieves stress... Plus I'm an aquarius. 

🥑Eating healthy is essential for memory, mood and focus. 

💦Sweating boosts energy and increases production of endorphins like serotonin and dopamine.

📖Reading improves your brain connectivity.

🏃🏼‍♀️Endurance training develops mental fortitude. It helps you overcome self-limiting thoughts and sharpens your memory. 

🛼Cardio activites a molecule called brain-derived neurotrophic factor, which repairs and creates brain cells. 

⏳Spending time by yourself builds your mental strength. It forces you to face yourself, grow and learn to love who you are. 

🌞Not only does soaking up the sun boost energy, it's natural d plays a big role in maintaining cognitive function.

🥾Hiking promotes creative thinking and increases attention span. Being in the fresh air also raises oxygen levels in the brain. 

🧘🏼‍♀️Yoga strengthens parts of the brain that play a key role is memory, attention, awareness and communion.

🙏Personal reflection and prayer makes a profound impact on our brains. It enhances our social awarness and empathy. This heightens our compassion and subsides negative emotions. Spread love. 

🤭And as you know... Laughter is the best medicine. 

⚖️Take care of your mind and your body will thank you, take care of your body and your mind will thank you💯
